title: #142: The State Of Union Of Conspiracies Withe Henry Zebrowski
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sm Tripoli! This episode we welcome from the "Last Podcast On The Left" and "Your Pretty Face Is Going To Hell," Henry Zebrowski. Lately we have been some really hard hitting subjects on the show so this episode we just decided to talk the state of the world of conspiracies!
Please check out my special "Zero Fucks" at Vimeo.com/ondemand/ZeroFucks
